OL,3,CGovernment admits it 'must do better'
OL,4,Cto improve infrastructure
OL,6,FRoad networks in Jersey have not
OL,7,Freceived enough investment over recent
OL,8,Fyears to keep them in an adequate
OL,9,Fcondition, a new report has revealed.
OL,11,FThe review by the island's chief
OL,12,Fauditor found that funding fell short
OL,13,Fof the "desirable level" required to
OL,14,Fmaintain the highways.
OL,16,FJersey's Infrastructure Minister,
OL,17,FConstable Andy Jehan, said: "Clearly,
OL,18,Fwe need to invest more in our
OL,19,Finfrastructure, be that above or below
OL,20,Fthe ground.
