OL,3,CGovernment admits it 'must do better'
OL,4,Cto improve infrastructure
OL,6,F"We can and we must do better."
OL,8,FHowever, he added: "Whilst we want to
OL,9,Fimprove the quality of the roads, I
OL,10,Fthink when we compare ours to other
OL,11,Fjurisdictions, whether that's the UK
OL,12,For Europe, we have a good standard."
OL,14,FMeanwhile, the infrastructure report
OL,15,Foutlined that the pilot scheme for an
OL,16,Feast-to-west bus service, Route 10, is
OL,17,Fexpected to cost #180,000 for the
OL,18,Fyear, with funding from the Climate
OL,19,FEmergency Fund.
