OL,6,FThe review's author, Comptroller and
OL,7,FAuditor General (C&AG) Lynn Pamment,
OL,8,Fquestioned whether the use of the
OL,9,Fmoney for the new cross-island route
OL,10,Faligns with the Fund's aims and
OL,11,Fexpressed concerns over whether it
OL,12,Frepresents value for money.
OL,14,FConstable Jehan said: "There's no way
OL,15,Fof getting from the west of the island
OL,16,Fto the east. Since the Enid Quenault
OL,17,FCentre opened at St Brelades, I've
OL,18,Fseen parishioners in St John, Trinity
OL,19,Fand St Mary's struggle to get to their
OL,20,Fappointments.
