OL,6,F"We need to have some form of
OL,7,Ftransport to get islanders across the
OL,8,Fnorth of the island and so I'm really
OL,9,Fpleased to see the trial of route 10."
OL,11,FConcerns over air resilience
OL,13,FThe report also highlighted issues
OL,14,Faround resilience with the reliance on
OL,15,FBlue Islands' limited fleet of five
OL,16,Faircraft, while raising concerns about
OL,17,Fthe air ambulance service not always
OL,18,Fbeing available.
