OL,6,FThe delays and cancellations of Blue
OL,7,FIslands' flights have come under
OL,8,Fscrutiny in recent months.
OL,10,FMeanwhile, Mark Boleat from the
OL,11,Findependent think tank Jersey Policy
OL,12,FCentre said the air ambulance part of
OL,13,Fthe report shows the most worrying
OL,14,Fissues.
OL,16,FHe explained: "There should have been
OL,17,Fa tender in advance and there wasn't.
OL,18,FThere's no proper monitoring - there
OL,19,Fwas a time when the service wasn't
OL,20,Favailable."
