OL,6,FNo ferry risk assessment
OL,8,FThe report also revealed that there
OL,9,Fwere no formal risk assessments
OL,10,Fcompleted around certain aspects of
OL,11,Fthe 20-year agreement with the
OL,12,Fisland's ferry provider, DFDS Seaways
OL,13,F- specifically around the exclusion of
OL,14,Finter-island services.
OL,16,FIt also outlined that the States are
OL,17,Fcommitted to an exclusive provider for
OL,18,Fa third longer than was originally
OL,19,Fspecified.
