OL,3,CGovernment admits it 'must do better'
OL,4,Cto improve infrastructure
OL,6,FJust last week, DFDS Seaways announced
OL,7,Fthere will be no high-speed ferry
OL,8,Fservice to the UK between November and
OL,9,Fthe end of April - in a major blow to
OL,10,Ftravellers who rely on the faster
OL,11,FPoole sailings.
OL,13,FChris Parker, Jersey Route Director,
OL,14,Fapologised for the timetable, but
OL,15,Fadded that capacity is "well above the
OL,16,Fhistorical demand for these services
OL,17,Fover the winter".
