OL,3,CGovernment admits it 'must do better'
OL,4,Cto improve infrastructure
OL,6,FHe explained: "Our winter timetable is
OL,7,Fdesigned to meet demand while
OL,8,Fdelivering a dependable service for
OL,9,Fislanders.
OL,11,F"Between November and March, we will
OL,12,Fbe offering capacity for up to 77,000
OL,13,Fpassengers to travel between Jersey
OL,14,Fand the UK, and up to 134,000
OL,15,Fpassengers between Jersey and France.
OL,17,F"We are focusing on delivering a long-
OL,18,Fterm sustainable service for Jersey,
OL,19,Fincluding investment in future tonnage
OL,20,Ffor the island."
